      "span_text": "From this a general conclusion can be made, that for an estimation of the Young's modulus of rubber material to use with the finite-element analysis, it is possible to adapt the rubber dimensions to obtain a shape factor of around 0.5 and use the simplest Eq. (10) developed by Gent and Lindley"
